rows.label: tlk42100151_03_msg0001
rows.name:
I recently met a Phonex from another
country the other day.

rows.label: tlk42100151_03_msg0002
rows.name:
They snuck onto a Divine Beast ship and
made shore at Port Anangham.

rows.label: tlk42100151_03_msg0003
rows.name:
I was so surprised! In terms of physical
stature, they looked just like me!

rows.label: tlk42100151_03_msg0004
rows.name:
I was so sure we were much thinner
than other Phonex, our living here in
Superbia, but there you go!

rows.label: tlk42100151_03_msg0005
rows.name:
It just goes to show that we can adapt
to any kind of climate, be it cold, hot,
humid or arid!
